%% ModelMesh Serving - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant REST as REST Proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh Sidecar<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/MLServer)
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, Runtime: Flow 1: REST Model Inference
    Client->>OAuth: HTTPS POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: OpenShift OAuth Bearer Token + SAR
    OAuth->>REST: HTTP (localhost)<br/>No auth (internal)
    REST->>MM: gRPC inference request<br/>Optional TLS
    MM->>Runtime: gRPC (TCP/Unix socket)<br/>plaintext (internal)
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
    MM-->>REST: gRPC response
    REST-->>OAuth: HTTP response
    OAuth-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Client, Runtime: Flow 2: gRPC Model Inference
    Client->>MM: gRPC via headless Service<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    MM->>Runtime: gRPC (TCP/Unix socket)<br/>plaintext
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
    MM-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over MM, etcd: Flow 3: Model Registration
    participant PReconciler as PredictorReconciler
    PReconciler->>MM: gRPC registerModel/setVModel<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS
    MM->>etcd: Store model placement state<br/>2379/TCP, Password auth
    etcd-->>MM: Acknowledgment
    MM-->>PReconciler: Registration confirmed

    Note over S3, Runtime: Flow 4: Model Artifact Download
    participant Puller as Storage Helper (Puller)
    Puller->>S3: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: storage-config credentials
    S3-->>Puller: Model files
    Puller->>Runtime: gRPC model load notification<br/>8086/TCP, plaintext

    Note over K8sAPI, PReconciler: Flow 5: ServingRuntime Reconciliation
    participant SRReconciler as ServingRuntimeReconciler
    SRReconciler->>K8sAPI: Watch ServingRuntime/ClusterServingRuntime CRs<br/>443/TCP, TLS, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>SRReconciler: CR event (create/update/delete)
    SRReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>(ModelMesh + Runtime + Sidecars)
    SRReconciler->>K8sAPI: Copy etcd secret to namespace
